proton-drive (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * SRP-6a authentication with 2FA support.
  * Two-way file synchronisation with Proton Drive.
  * Unix socket IPC between protond, proton-drive CLI and proton-gui.
  * System tray icon support (tray feature).
  * Transfer scheduling and pause/resume.
  * Conflict detection and resolution.

